[normal]&#xa0;[bold]ANNEX D[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]1.[bold]              [bold]COUNTRIES IN THE EUROPEAN UNION[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]Once registered to vote, nationals of the Republic of Ireland can vote in all elections. Once registered to vote, the nationals of the other European Union countries can vote in all elections, apart from general elections for the U.K. parliament.
